description: U.S. Secretary of State Antony Blinken (R) steps off a plane upon arrival to Amman, Jordan, on Oct. 12, 2023. Mr. Blinken was to visit Saudi Arabia, Egypt, the UAE, Qatar and Jordan to put pressure on Hamas and secure the release of hostages, told reporters later the images were "new evidence of depravity and the inhumanity of Hamas".
